{"tid":1178530,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"在線上 係種好遙遠既距離","createTime":"2019-05-30T13:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T13:39:58.000Z","uid":16425,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d02ef11b2c189b1c6c72a41bb66e266800e560d2","tid":1178530,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"見到在線中 有時會有種好近既感覺<br />\n因為你知道同一時間佢都睇緊電話<br />\n<br />\n但同時 都係好遙遠既感覺<br />\n當你搵佢既時候 佢偏係唔覆你<br />\n甚至可能online多幾次先覆下你<br />\n<br />\n見到呢三個字 係令人又愛又狠既感覺黎<br />\n你係閒人先會有呢種感覺<br />\n所以 要搵多啲野充實時間 <br />\n唔好將重心放係呢三個字到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb5ad17481329609a7db53d0ce490a514a509aa","tid":1178530,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:13:08.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"c294ee7361112810acfec29629ff8c7fa7c82fdd","tid":1178530,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"7511aa0eaef108ba67218048520c3040f52ada88","tid":1178530,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"Noted"},{"pid":"ac6d9927d5ca28545b8ccb62b9798340e9af0cf7","tid":1178530,"uid":217899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"你同我距離較遠啦 又唔見你攞嚟講 又唔係每一個在線上都係咁遠 你咪搵啲近啲嘅囉 你唔係緊張人哋 近定遠又關你叉事咩 人哋又唔係你條女就將啲心思擺係人哋度 自己攞苦嚟辛攞架嚟丟 一切都係因為你自己戇鳩啫 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢番說話我都想同十年前嘅自己講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3850d804df777584288537a15743fb23d179c9","tid":1178530,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6d9927d5ca28545b8ccb62b9798340e9af0cf7","tid":1178530,"uid":217899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"你同我距離較遠啦 又唔見你攞